cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DM, cs.SI, cs.CL 

The paper presents an extension of the affinity propagation clustering algorithm to solve the hierarchical clustering problem. This makes it relevant to several sub-categories of computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data mining (cs.DM), social and information networks (cs.SI), and computational linguistics (cs.CL). However, given the focus on clustering and optimization, cs.LG and cs.AI are the most likely sub-categories.
